My profile was rejected. How do find out why so I could correct it

I'm sorry to hear that your profile was rejected. The rejection usually happens when the business details provided cannot be verified with our sources. To resolve this, please ensure that all the information you provided matches a legitimate business entity. If you need further assistance, feel free to email adsupport@newsbreak.com for more detailed guidance.
Where do I go to do the correction?

To correct your profile information, you should first gather any additional documentation that can help verify your business details. Then, reach out to our Ad Support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with the updated information. They will guide you through the process of resubmitting your profile for verification.
